author: Tom O'Connor
title: Why U.S. and China Can't Team Up to Defeat the Coronavirus Outbreak
description: While the United States and the Soviet Union banded together in World War II, experts say the U.S. and China's economic superpower rivalry runs too deep for them to cooperate against the new coronavirus.
